data.description: In Douglas, Georgia's Baymeadows Estates, a lovely home is just waiting for its next owner. It offers a bonus room, a fenced-in backyard, a spacious two-car garage, a walk-in laundry room, and a sizable pantry. The house was built in 2021. The master bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet, soaking tub, walk-in shower, and separate toilet. The house is located on a lovely lot with access to the Baymeadows Lake, which is close by. There is always something to do at Baymeadows Lake with aquatic activities. The frantic activity of Douglas' town center is nearby. Jacksonville International Airport is about two hours away. The beaches are about two hours away.
